reviewText: u can never go wrong with a drew barrymore movie. never been kissed... i cry everytime!
I ordered these for my granddaughter.  She had asked for Ever After. When I saw all three movies could be bought on one DVD I got them for her.  She liked them all.
My daughter asked for one of the movies, but I knew she liked all of them so this pack was a perfect gift. I was right. She loved this set of DVDs!
I liked all three movies, Ever After being my favorite, I can see myself watching it again and again. Definitely chic flicks.
The disks were more scratch than I expected but they still play without skipping.  But when you buy used items, you really can't expect the best. They still play without skipping so I'm satisfied.
I love the idea of having three movies in one pack of your favorite actor or actress...awesome.
